a5d3b296-9fda-4a8b-8122-9bebfe43522f Place cubes in a single layer on a cookie sheet. Freeze until firm, about 1-2 hours.

a5d3b296-9fda-4a8b-8122-9bebfe43522f Place almond bark in a large glass bowl or measuring cup. Microwave on High for 90 seconds; stir. Continue microwaving in 15 second intervals, stirring after each, until melted and smooth.
